phs and the increasing availability of\nrobotic telescopes.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Tue, 7 Apr 2020 16:09:02 GMT"},{"version":"v2","created":"Sat, 11 Apr 2020 03:13:16 GMT"}],"update_date":"2020-04-14"}
